# Changelog

## [0.9.0] - 2024-12-01
### Added
- Stage S3 input files as part of the flow to ensure remote workers have data locally.
- Accelerator-aware scheduling support.
- Job lock to prevent concurrent races on the same job.
- Multi-node scaling (preview) for larger workloads.
- Prebuilt container image deploy flow for Kubernetes targets.
- Support running across multiple compartments/subnets for better scalability.
- Helper tools moved under `tools/` in this module for OCI and workflow debugging.

### Changed
- Split job submission, monitoring, and result handling into clearer phases.
- Improved stability under load and more robust kill handling.
- Clean up failure workspaces to reduce residue between runs.
